name: "GONZO" APE #3
description:
Gonzo is made to kill. He injured one eye, 
he was injured in a fight with a man, because of this, 
Gonzo sees only three colors - black, white and red.
 
Impulsive, not sociable, very cunning, 
and has great authority among other apes,
has great success with a female, father of 74 children.

He owns many combat techniques, knows how to control almost 
any enemy technique of a person.

Hates Mojo.




- "A man sounds proudly, a monkey sounds promising."
